Drools and jBPM5 Community Training Course Example Projects

In this repository you can find multiple examples and hands on labs related with the community training course of jBPM5 and Drools.
You can find the slides for the different modules in:
http://salaboy.wordpress.com/

All the example projects where created using Maven and you can open them with your favorite IDE. 

For building the projects you can, from the root directory run:
mvn clean install


jBPM5 Community Training Course

jBPM5 Training Roadmap: http://salaboy.wordpress.com/2011/01/24/announcing-jbpm5-community-training/

Module #1: jBPM5 Overview: http://salaboy.wordpress.com/2011/01/29/jbpm5-community-training-module-1-jbpm5-introduction/

Module #2: The BPM Practice: http://salaboy.wordpress.com/2011/02/04/jbpm5-community-training-%E2%80%93-module-2-the-bpm-practice/

Module #3: Delayed

Module #4: jBPM5 APIs : http://salaboy.wordpress.com/2011/02/21/jbpm5-community-training-%E2%80%93-module-4-the-jbpm5-api-overview/

The Example from these modules can be found inside the jbpm5/ directory of this repository.

